- Start‑to‑finish sequencing and narrative: I like album‑style listening and sequencing that highlights pacing and vocal nuance. This candidate’s “expansive, continuous narrative across lengthy tracks” is designed for that kind of engagement — it encourages attentive, repeated listens and rewards close, dynamic playback.
