Why I choose the Prince compilation
- Matches rhythmic immediacy and punch: The Prince compilation is described as “tight funk,” with punchy restrained rhythms, elastic bass and percussive guitars. That directly aligns with my preference for drums locked to bass, clear rhythmic drive and mixes that preserve transient snap and momentum.
